<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
 <head>
   <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
 </head>
 <body>
   <center><h4>Your on duty request has been rejected</h4></center> 

    <p> Your on duty request has been rejected by<b> <%= @od_request.employee.first_name.to_s+' '+@od_request.employee.last_name.to_s %> from date <%= @od_request.start_date.to_date %>To<%= @od_request.end_date.to_date%>.</b></p>

     <center><h4>Details of the on duty :-</h4></center>
     <p>Total Number of days :- <%= @od_request.no_of_day %></p>
     <p> On duty reason : <%= @od_request.reason %></p>

    <h4>Requester Details:-</h4>
    
    <p> Employee ID:- <%= @od_request.employee.try(:manual_employee_code)%></p>

    <p> Employee Name:- <%= @od_request.employee.try(:first_name)%> <%= @od_request.employee.try(:middle_name)%> <%= @od_request.employee.try(:last_name)%></p>
   </p>
 </body>
</html>
